curam.util.ieg.impl
Class QuestionResult

java.lang.Object
  curam.util.ieg.impl.QuestionResult

public class QuestionResult
extends java.lang.Object

The QuestionResult class represents a summary of a question that has appeared on a question page during script execution. The question results do not include any of the textual elements of the questions, just the answers.
